name: IDOT: Thoughtful Chaos
description:
A collection of moments in @idot's workspace from October 2020 to April 2021! In here you'll find:

  • Silly doodles
  • Thoughtful notes
  • Weird brainstorms
  • McDonalds burger bun?


Mostly, this is a fun record of internal moments we've shared that have made it a little easier to work together - despite having never met each other.


Published for Config 2021. Learn more about this project at Config!
